56
00:05:22,604 --> 00:05:27,476
♬｢Grab your coat,  grab your hat baby｣

57
00:05:27,476 --> 00:05:31,313
♬｢Leave your worries on the doorstep｣

58
00:05:31,313 --> 00:05:34,083
♬｢Just direct your feet｣

59
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:37,920
♬｢On the sunny side of the street｣

60
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:41,757
♬｢Can't you hear that pitter-pat？｣

61
00:05:41,757 --> 00:05:46,095
♬｢That happy tune is your step｣

62
00:05:46,095 --> 00:05:49,131
♬｢Life can be so sweet｣

63
00:05:49,131 --> 00:06:06,448
♬～

64
00:06:06,448 --> 00:06:11,587
♬｢I used to walk in the shade｣

65
00:06:11,587 --> 00:06:15,457
♬｢With those blues on parade｣

66
00:06:15,457 --> 00:06:19,128
♬｢But I'm not afraid｣

67
